{"tid":2224052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國可以禁止中國代表入場聯合國開會？","createTime":"2020-09-30T09:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T04:21:39.000Z","uid":4672,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1a0e440f9c5dbcadc37374cea5da97dffac0f3","tid":2224052,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:01:53.000Z","msg":"from wiki<br />\n聯合國總部大樓（亦稱聯合國大廈）是聯合國總部的所在地，位於美國紐約市曼哈頓區東側，屬於國際領土，因此只要是會員國國民持有護照就可以進入。<br />\n<br />\n開會地點係美國紐約曼哈頓區 <br />\n咁係咪只要取消支那代表/俄羅斯代表護照 就可以禁止支那代表入安理會開會<br />\n從而直接通過制裁/出兵中國之類議案？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfea3f22eca57d6e2bdf131d988ea6165636e97","tid":2224052,"uid":57671,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f642c15e7c6cf860751225da5437e62f88fd213c","tid":2224052,"uid":15605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"如果係支那就鍾意搞呢啲小動作，美國佬最多咪退出自己搞"},{"pid":"5db7aa97e2cbb52aa84992bf56d49835684e19e6","tid":2224052,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f642c15e7c6cf860751225da5437e62f88fd213c","tid":2224052,"uid":15605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"如果係支那就鍾意搞呢啲小動作，美國佬最多咪退出自己搞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"美國以前成deny人地visa連境都入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85ab1b5773ae0919e443feeeb1639a7367425a5","tid":2224052,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"其實聯合國總部唔係應該設喺中立國例如瑞士之類?"},{"pid":"b3e20074f2eada8593ba413538afaf50713230b0","tid":2224052,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"可以唔比簽證中國"},{"pid":"272956dd8067472e30f2188912c8c20612b4e6af","tid":2224052,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"聯合國本身就唔會阻到美國出兵同制裁"},{"pid":"9ad1315c8eec498f2ef4eea9af69b289dd0ab5bb","tid":2224052,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"主席配合你表決先得"},{"pid":"16baeeb33fe33d5aeebb3741217747ed542fec72","tid":2224052,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b85ab1b5773ae0919e443feeeb1639a7367425a5","tid":2224052,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"其實聯合國總部唔係應該設喺中立國例如瑞士之類?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"以前國聯咪係瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩用？"},{"pid":"b1e51c3606f237b2a25ddb0ecc9b205b5e7c7060","tid":2224052,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"272956dd8067472e30f2188912c8c20612b4e6af","tid":2224052,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"聯合國本身就唔會阻到美國出兵同制裁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:32:13.000Z","msg":"問題係美國總統出兵發動戰爭只有60日時間<br />\n因為憲法規定宣戰權屬於國會 總統只係軍隊總指揮官<br />\n如果國會唔通過出兵法案 60日後美軍就要收隊<br />\n<br />\n但聯合國法案曾經被美國國會通過 有合法權力來源<br />\n所以係聯合國安理會通過的出兵法案 無須國會同意<br />\n唯一可以繞過國會發動合法發動戰爭方法<br />\n不過此方法下美軍要以 &ldquo;聯合國軍隊&rdquo; 名義出兵 唔可以用美國軍隊名義"},{"pid":"02b686ebb307e2ed35b825a86311584e679cca35","tid":2224052,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:34:05.000Z","msg":"有大使館㗎嘛,點會阻到."},{"pid":"67574857e156f3faf56e31aeddf4cea25110cc21","tid":2224052,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:34:39.000Z","msg":"空降咪得囉"},{"pid":"f84c06b08b74f0489a43388dfb0c3010a4f685bc","tid":2224052,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"有UN passport"},{"pid":"bfd28bd21ec0433c951033edcff928e9f27e6d11","tid":2224052,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ad1315c8eec498f2ef4eea9af69b289dd0ab5bb","tid":2224052,"uid":1654,"like":